    "body": "They are not looking to do any fixes for foundryup because of the native (rust) replacement, but I went ahead and addressed it \r\n\r\n\r\n```diff\r\n- curl -# -L $BIN_URL -o $BIN_PATH\r\n+ readonly CURL_FLAGS=\"${CURL_FLAGS:- -vvv --max-time 120 --retry 3 --fail}\"\r\n\r\n+# we deliberately don't quote CURL_FLAGS\r\n+# shellcheck disable=SC2086 \r\n+curl ${CURL_FLAGS}  \"${BIN_UR}\" -o \"${BIN_PATH}\"\r\n+if ! $? -ne 0; then\r\n+\t>&2 echo \"Error: failed to download! code $?\"\r\n+\texit 2\r\n+fi\r\n```\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/pull/2221/files#diff-79a844de4d6869f243ecd1e7ca4d9532d9a4987f85ca63d9f4af85aa227ecb38L15-R23",
